{"tid":1847961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：請香港人盡快從中國回港","createTime":"2020-01-28T09:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T09:11:00.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e07b537045cd129c58cc72391ef7a254ec9a66bd","tid":1847961,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:10:11.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥呼籲港人盡快從內地回港，並在條件許可下，在回港14日內留在家中，如要外出要戴口罩，並不要再到有疫情的地方，亦要因為不用上班和上學多了外遊。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，需要進一步減少境內人流，政府已經公佈，政府公務員可以在明天起在家工作至2月2日，緊急服務會維持。她又再次呼籲市民在乘搭公共交通工具時戴口罩。"},{"pid":"534e7be4a97bd113b29d8ac29d00ee43e07dc4da","tid":1847961,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:10:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1256612&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1256612%26csid%3D261_341&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=29a9e26d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1256612&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"d1692b7dc217d5d72ed93779a6960d5aa860cd6a","tid":1847961,"uid":38528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"快D返黎返工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6849adde3d059e93c22d300f84c392f64e54b3","tid":1847961,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:11:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=b077cfcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <